Package ZetaFish.NetworkObjects

Class ZetaFish.NetworkObjects.ZFCard extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

Serialized Fields

suit

ZFCard.Suits suit
This card's suit, one of the constants SPADES, HEARTS, DIAMONDS, CLUBS, or JOKER. The suit cannot be changed after the card is constructed.

value

int value
The card's value. For a normal cards, this is one of the values 1 through 13, with 1 representing ACE. For a JOKER, the value can be anything. The value cannot be changed after the card is constructed.
